import React from 'react';
import {
    Typography,
    Grid,
    Card,
    CardHeader,
    CardMedia,
    CardContent,
    CardActions,
    Avatar,
    IconButton,
} from '@material-ui/core'
import './Home.css'


function Home() {
    return(
      <>
        <Grid container spacing={3} className="main">
            <Grid item xs={6}>
                <Card>
                    <CardHeader>
                        <Typography variant="h5">Nome do Filme</Typography>
                    </CardHeader>
                    <CardMedia />
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Descrição do filme</Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                    <CardActions disableSpacing>
                    </CardActions>
                </Card>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </>  
    );
  }
  
  export default Home;
